fullDescription.text:
The AWS Athena Workgroup is unencrypted. Encryption protects query results in your workgroup. To enable, add: `encryption_configuration {
  encryption_option = "SSE_KMS"
  kms_key_arn       = aws_kms_key.example.arn
}` within `result_configuration { }` in your resource block, where `encryption_option` is your chosen encryption method and `kms_key_arn` is your KMS key ARN.

